name: Resting in Peace?
description:
An old section of Saint John-at-Hampstead Churchyard, London. It was peaceful enough during the day, but as twilight began to fall, a spooky feeling set in.

Was that just a flaw in the film at the bottom, or did I catch a spirit rising from the grave, embarking on its evening stroll around the headstones?

35 mm film, c. 2000
